column5: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7qb0vquRcys  Look at the first little girls attitude just at the end. She looks pissed
There must be something wrong with me cause I found it sad.
I like the one where he gives the little boy a really neat toy truck and then snatches it away and replaces it, the kid says "That's a piece of junk. The look on the kids face is amazing!
Ha ha ya I have seen that one on tv before.. I wonder where she gets those looks from? Hmmm I dont even know her mom but could you imaging living with her???
They're running those commercials on TV down here.  I agree, the one with the little boy and the truck is a classic.   "It's a piece of junk'.    I love it.
